===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*sri||to exist}} ({{zh-ref|Benedict, 1976}}); cognate with {{cog|tbq-pro|*s-ri(t)}}, whence {{cog|bo|སྲིད་པ}} and {{cog|my|ရှိ||to be, to exist}}.

{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} derives {{cog|sit-pro|*sreŋ||live, alive, green, raw}} from this root, yet points out that {{och-l|生}}'s initial '''*sr-''' cluster was retained instead of becoming voiceless /r̥/ as in {{och-l|體}}, possibly owing to re-analysis of '''*s-''' as a causative prefix.

